    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Description], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[Price], [p].[Quantity], [p].[Rating], [p].[SubCatagoryId], [p].[Title], [p].[UserId], [p].[View]
    FROM [Product] AS [p]
    WHERE [p].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit) AND [p].[UserId] = @__userId_0
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_1 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_2 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN [SubCatagory] AS [s] ON [t].[SubCatagoryId] = [s].[Id]
